Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{title}Showdown
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Romero...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.49,0:01:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Romero, let me bring you there...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.75,0:01:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place you longed for.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.78,0:01:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A place where no one can catch up with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.11,0:02:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At a speed fast enough to brush off the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to reach there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.51,0:02:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you've got work this late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.31,0:02:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For my work it doesn't matter what time it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting tired of becoming an assassin?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This might take a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.59,0:02:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll stay up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.56,0:02:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I picked up a broken video cassette recorder during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.67,0:02:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to try to fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just buy a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.36,0:02:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's such a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.82,0:02:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it can still be used.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can still be used, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.20,0:02:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.29,0:03:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.04,0:03:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.41,0:03:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to leave you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.29,0:03:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay by your side forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can still return to the way I once was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.11,0:03:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's time to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether I choose to stop or to run...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever I pick, the organization will...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.95,0:03:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Lizzie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lizzie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lizzie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.04,0:04:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always giving you trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.11,0:04:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard about it, brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're that Phantom guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder my young men were finished off so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got solid proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.38,0:04:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.42,0:04:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That picture... who...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.12,0:04:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not gonna defend yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.66,0:04:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Godoh, it's a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.46,0:04:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.76,0:04:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me before you embarrass yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:05:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know your higher-ups ordered you to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just want to know the inside story.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.39,0:05:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one behind all three attacks against us was Claudia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you fuckin' stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much effort do you think Claudia put in to get you guys into Inferno?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.73,0:05:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I like loyal people,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.19,0:05:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that woman doesn't deserve so much loyalty from you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.62,0:05:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She tricked us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both you guys and us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.99,0:05:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the fuck up...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't our first time meeting at this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was such a memorable night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's almost been a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.88,0:05:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A year?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.68,0:06:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which organization are they from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.14,0:06:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lading...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early to say that, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just get the hell out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So it was you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You teamed up with Scythe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anyone named Scythe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who planned it was Claudia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.71,0:06:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we were about to hit a dead end...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman came to us out of the blue and offered a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She allowed us to steal 500 kg of cocaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She prepared everything beforehand, including backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She even asked us, "Do you want to have some 'fun' in Los Angeles?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did she do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.78,0:07:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The condition was that after things were settled,\Nthe Godoh Group would join Inferno through her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.89,0:07:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At first we didn't understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but after finding out her situation, we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.35,0:07:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wants an organization within Inferno that can watch her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she's always alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she won't have a chance to shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.33,0:07:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing about how we used to get cargo from other places is bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.14,0:07:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The market we have now was created in the course of one year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using the cocaine we stole from you as capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Claudia sold out Scythe...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.03,0:07:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, there was a retard who got screwed from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.75,0:07:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it him? The Scythe you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.57,0:07:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:08:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's been a sudden change of plans. Scythe betrayed the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He made Phantom attack Inferno's lading.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.59,0:08:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The organization is looking for those two with all their might.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.51,0:08:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They haven't found either of them though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.90,0:08:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A way to prove your innocence and get Ein back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how to use this, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all because of her...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.31,0:08:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scythe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.96,0:08:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, we were hurt and shed tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging by your looks, it seems like you remembered something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true, Phantom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like even the great Phantom was deceived by a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, there's a sequel to the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.65,0:09:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bitch wants to kill Shiga and me in the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and control the Godoh Group by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.85,0:09:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On one hand, she's finishing us off in order to seal our mouths.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other, she's using the confusion that's caused to remove her rivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I can't believe how scheming she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.28,0:09:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it? She used us as stepping stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give a shit about Inferno anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name won't be Godoh Daisuke if I don't do anything after being deceived like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe this! I don't fuckin' believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fucking bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.68,0:09:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.90,0:10:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get on, Phantom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.71,0:10:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go on first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.26,0:10:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elen...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.47,0:10:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elen...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible... you're still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.19,0:11:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Elen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.15,0:11:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me Elen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.71,0:11:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now and in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.41,0:11:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just been Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.02,0:11:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inferno will come and kill you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.18,0:11:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.24,0:11:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inferno will?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.39,0:11:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.46,0:11:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now and in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.09,0:12:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scythe Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.60,0:12:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Godoh Group, Claudia McCunnen,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Inferno's Issac Wisemel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stirring up a three-sided struggle of fear and doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sending the ones who tricked you before to hell one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.47,0:12:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth behind it was sent to Inferno through my guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.17,0:12:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll take action soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll kill the traitor, Claudia McCunnen...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.82,0:13:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and her trusted subordinate, Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The organization is going to kill me? If so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You passed the entrance exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.60,0:13:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.16,0:13:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to tell you right away.\NAm I interfering with your work?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.63,0:13:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.13,0:13:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But foreign trading is tiring, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to leave Japan the day after tomorrow to deliver stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want any gifts?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's fine since you always buy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.54,0:13:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if I receive too much from you, mom will find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.88,0:13:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.26,0:14:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My friends are waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.79,0:14:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.71,0:14:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although she was kept apart from the main family,\Nthe same blood of me and the boss flows inside Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The blood of the Godoh's demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.37,0:14:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone tries to take advantage of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.89,0:14:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio won't be able to protect herself since she doesn't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter that her standpoint or surname changed,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she's still my little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My precious little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiga, this is going to be a huge deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't make it back alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Shiga, will watch over Mio-san's future until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Shiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got shot in the stomach and shoulder, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.65,0:15:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.74,0:15:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've survived after catching at least twice as many bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.93,0:15:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Asura realm is my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:15:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.40,0:16:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's left?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.27,0:16:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.21,0:16:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? So in the end,\Nthe only ones left are you and me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.49,0:16:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of what hell it is,\N you're always there to rush in with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With my courage and your intelligence, no matter when...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.07,0:16:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what about Claudia?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inferno is going to finish that woman off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.43,0:17:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget that. The problem is with us, the Godoh Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inferno won't let us, the group that was under that woman, go so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.70,0:17:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,War is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inferno, so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.11,0:17:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They tricked us, so it's payback time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to teach them a lesson, right Shiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.01,0:17:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll kill them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.87,0:17:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as one person dies, everything will be settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.56,0:17:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you won't believe me no matter what I say now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.16,0:17:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro, I truly love you from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.23,0:18:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Killing the traitors proves the Godoh Group's sincerity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.63,0:18:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you out with joining Inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.90,0:18:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Shiga, now the Godoh Group is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.86,0:18:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giuseppe, I can barely hold back my urge to shoot you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.54,0:18:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to shoot me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.47,0:18:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like we'll get along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.29,0:19:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can become good friends, Mr. Shiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clau... Where are you, Clau?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.16,0:19:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?! Where the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.57,0:19:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least give me an excuse, Claudia McCunnen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.97,0:19:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.25,0:19:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any pursuers?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.97,0:19:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still not bored of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.12,0:19:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.68,0:20:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like that song that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.07,0:20:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it was given to me by the person I love most.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I had nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.49,0:20:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What normal people usually have, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.06,0:20:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I thought I'd never be able to get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.99,0:20:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.77,0:20:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay by your side forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.40,0:21:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.35,0:21:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.81,0:21:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CAL!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.27,0:23:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this world isn't an endless hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.09,0:23:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it must be because you're here alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.29,0:23:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
